title: Hamburger Pie
directions: Brown hamburger and onion together until hamburger is fully cooked. Drain fat.
Add tomato sauce, green beans, salt and garlic sauce. Stir and let simmer on low while you prepare the pie.
Unroll the cresecent roll dough and spread over the bottoms and sides of a 9" pie pan.
Combine beaten egg and 1 Cup of cheese and spread over bottom of crust.
Spoon hot ground beef mixture onto crust.
Bake in preheated oven at 375 degrees Fahrenheit for 15 - 20 minutes.
